🔴 A surveillance camera captured a clip of a person who entered through the luggage compartment behind the Sheremetyevo airport building in Russia 🇷🇺 and struggled to enter the main hall by force from this place.

 - According to the trader, he was afraid of flying, so he drank to get rid of the ghost of fear, but he lost the main door when he arrived.

 🔺 The drunk is 27 years old, and airport security caught him later and was investigated.

 In the end, they fined him 5,000 rubles‼️✈️ #piloteyes777 🎥: @aviatagse
